author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Harvia Finland received notification Danske Bank A/S, Finland Branch, acting as stabilising manager in offering
text:
April 20 (Reuters) - Harvia Finland Oy:
* RECEIVED NOTIFICATION THAT DANSKE BANK A/S, FINLAND BRANCH (“DANSKE BANK”), ACTING AS STABILISING MANAGER IN OFFERING
* RECEIVED NOTIFICATION THAT DANSKE BANK A/S, FINLAND BRANCH HAS CARRIED OUT STABILISATION MEASURES BETWEEN 16 APRIL 2018 AND 20 APRIL 2018
* HAS BEEN INFORMED BY DANSKE BANK THAT STABILISATION PERIOD HAS DISCONTINUED AND NO FURTHER STABILISATION MEASURES WILL BE UNDERTAKEN Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
